About
Time Out Market, created from scratch by Time Out Portugal, has all the very best under one roof in Lisbon. The market is home to top-notch restaurants, bars, a cooking school and a high-end music venue. Here, you can find some of the freshest fish, meat and fruit in town, try the tastiest local wine and dine at over 40 restaurants specializing in both Portuguese cuisine and food from around the world. Sit inside to enjoy the ambience of the century-old market or outside to bask in the Lisbon sun. You can easily reach the market with the Lisbon Metro. â€“ Tripadvisor
